0) grafana data show nai kr raha hai data source add krne k baad bhi it shows "datasource ${DS_PROMETHEUS} was not found"
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
    - after adding the datasource and dashboard in grafana if is shows errors "datasource ${DS_PROMETHEUS} was not found" while hovering
      the mouse over the tabs. 
    - then go "EDIT" which you will find in the secound line in the top right corner.
    - then "SETTINGS".
    - then "JSON MODEL".
    - then in the editor right click and find "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" and uske sath se arrow hoga for replace click that and apne "datasource" 
      ka name likho jo tumne diya hoga at the starting jb data source add kiya tha mere case me "prometheus" hai.
    - then click replace all.
    - if your forgot your datasource name the click connections --> Data sources --> Name prometheus(you can see your name prometheus).
    - phir chalen lg jayega tumhara GRAFANA.
    - all this in one line:
            EDIT --> SETTINGS --> JSON MODEL --> change datasource
