1) errors ka mtlb while Configuring the /etc/prometheus/prometheus.yml then blackbox ko start krte he jo-2 errors aayenge unka solution:
========================================================================================================================================
ye error show ho rahe the jb maine prometheus, granafna and jenkins ki entry /etc/prometheus.yml me kiya tha aur blackbox ko start kiya toh ye error aa raha tha:
