    time=2026-03-22T18:29:11.962Z level=WARN source=http.go:490 msg="Received redirect" module=http_2xx target=http://43.205.207.91:3000 location=/login
    time=2026-03-22T18:29:20.101Z level=ERROR source=http.go:585 msg="Error for HTTP request" module=http_2xx target=http://43.205.207.91:8080 err="Get \"http://43.205.207.91:8080\": dial tcp 43.205.207.91:8080: connect: connection refused"
    time=2026-03-22T18:29:20.101Z level=ERROR source=handler.go:130 msg="Probe failed" module=http_2xx target=http://43.205.207.91:8080 duration_seconds=0.001366818
    time=2026-03-22T18:29:26.961Z level=WARN source=http.go:490 msg="Received redirect" module=http_2xx target=http://43.205.207.91:3000 location=/login

MEANINGS:
    Error 1 — Received redirect
    target=http://43.205.207.91:3000 location=/login
    Matlab:
    Blackbox gaya   → http://43.205.207.91:3000 pe
    Server bola     → "Yahan mat jao, /login pe jao"
    Blackbox bola   → "Mujhe 200 OK chahiye tha, redirect mila"

    Simple: Grafana bina login ke access nahi deta

    Error 2 — Connection refused
    target=http://43.205.207.91:8080 connection refused
    Matlab:
    Blackbox gaya   → http://43.205.207.91:8080 pe
    Server bola     → "Koi nahi hai yahan" (port band hai)

    Simple: Us IP pe koi service nahi chal rahi port 8080 pe
        Jenkins wahan nahi hai

    Error 3 — Probe failed
    msg="Probe failed" duration_seconds=0.000727056
    Matlab:
    Blackbox ne check kiya → website
    Result aaya            → fail (200 OK nahi mila)

    Simple: Website check fail ho gayi

    How to read errors — Rule:
    level=INFO  → sab theek hai, sirf information
    level=WARN  → kuch galat hai but chal raha hai
    level=ERROR → kuch band hai ya fail ho gaya

    Aage kaise samjhoge:
    Har error mein 3 cheezein dekho:

    1. target = kaunsi website/IP check ho rahi thi
                target=http://43.205.207.91:8080
                → 43.205.207.91 IP ka port 8080

    2. msg = kya hua
            "connection refused" → port band hai
            "Received redirect"  → website redirect kar rahi hai
            "Probe failed"       → check fail hua

    3. err = exact reason
            dial tcp ... connection refused → server nahi mila
            location=/login                → login page pe bheja

    Simple dictionary:
    Error                               Matlab
    connection refused                  Port band hai ya service nahi chal rahi
    Received redirect                   Website aur page pe bhej rahi hai
    Probe failed                        Check fail hua
    timeout                             Server ne response nahi diya
    no such host                        Domain/IP exist nahi karta

