3) time=2026-03-22T18:37:11.961Z level=WARN source=http.go:490 msg="Received redirect" module=http_2xx target=http://43.205.207.91:3000 location=/login
          - iss error "Grafana login page pe redirect kar raha hai — isliye aa raha hai!"
          - TOH APKO Blackbox ME BHI CHANGES KRNE HOENGE. JO DEFINED HAI 3.1 ME.
          - Blackbox check karne gaya → http://43.205.207.91:3000
            Grafana ne bola           → "Pehle login karo" → /login
            Blackbox ne bola          → "Mujhe 200 OK chahiye tha!"
            Result                    → WARN ⚠️
          - # /etc/grafana/grafana.ini mein
                [auth.anonymous]
                enabled = true
          - if you are using the docker for grafana then this can't be channger you have to pass the envronment variable and then again
            start the new container.
          - # Naya container banao anonymous access ke saath
                docker run -d \
                --name grafana \
                -p 3000:3000 \
                -e GF_AUTH_ANONYMOUS_ENABLED=true \
                -e GF_AUTH_ANONYMOUS_ORG_ROLE=Viewer \
                grafana/grafana
          - -e GF_AUTH_ANONYMOUS_ORG_ROLE=Viewer
                # GF        = Grafana
                # AUTH      = Authentication  
                # ANONYMOUS = Bina login wala user
                # ORG_ROLE  = Organization mein role kya hoga
                # Viewer    = Sirf dekh sakta hai, edit nahi kar sakta
                ```

                ---

                **Yaad karne ka trick:**
                ```
                GF  = Grafana
                _   = ka / ki
                AUTH_ANONYMOUS_ENABLED = Authentication Anonymous Enabled

                Matlab → Grafana ki Anonymous Authentication Enable karo
                ```

                ---

                **Kya Docker image mein jaake directly change kar sakte hain?**
                ```
                Docker image  = Read only ❌ (change nahi ho sakta)
                Docker container = Chal raha hai, andar ja sakte ho ✅
